review.title: Perfect !!!
review.text: This 55 inch QLED exceeded our expectations. We are using it in a bedroom and the picture quality is outstanding. I used the same picture settings as my larger QLED and the 43 inch looks almost the same. Very satisfied with the Apps available. We also like the fact that you can go directly to Amazon Prime with a single button push on the remote. Overall, very satisfied with this product for the price.

review.title: Redline
review.text: As soon as I turned on this TV for the first time, I noticed a red in color vertical line showing from top to bottom about 10" from the left side of the screen. Unit was to be repaired by Samsung authorized service, but the part is not available. Samsung has promised to exchange. Still waiting on the details for the exchange.
